    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Designates ornamental plants grown indoors, other than in greenhouses, and adapting to less than ideal environmental conditions.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
